<table width="438" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" border="0">
<tr>
<td class="text8">丑"二"(阴阳)应于大地。为刚、柔，高、下，东、西，南、北。?</td>
</tr>
</table>
<table width="438" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" border="0">
