</tr>
</table>
<table width="438" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" border="0">
<tr>
<td class="text8">下面试论仁、义、礼之运用。?</td>
</tr>
</table>
<table width="438" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" border="0">
<tr>
<td class="text8"></td>
</tr>
